text: Shayna Powless (born January 8, 1994) is an American professional racing cyclist. She signed to ride for the UCI Women's Team for the 2019 women's road cycling season. She is the daughter of Olympic marathon runner Jen Allred and the sister of fellow racing cyclist Neilson Powless. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:American female cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
